266
0:14:47.434,000 --> 0:14:5,000
Help with the mass persuasion campaign that will start this spring.

267
0:14:50.843,000 --> 0:14:52,000
We have to change the minds of the American people.

268
0:14:53.375,000 --> 0:14:55,000
Because presently, the politicians do not have permission

269
0:14:56.158,000 --> 0:14:57,000
