0:15:19.555,000 --> 0:15:21,000
I like "climate crisis" instead of "climate collapse,"

276
0:15:22.448,000 --> 0:15:24,000
but again, those of you who are good at branding,

277
0:15:24.799,000 --> 0:15:25,000
I need your help on this.

278
0:15:26.768,000 --> 0:15:3,000
Somebody said the test we're facing now, a scientist told me,

279
0:15:30.892,000 --> 0:15:33,000
is whether the combination of an opposable thumb

280
0:15:34,000 --> 0:15:36,000
and a neocortex is a viable combination.

281
0:15:36.947,000 --> 0:15:37,000
(Laughter)

282
0:15:38.825,000 --> 0:15:39,000
That's really true.

283
0:15:43.16,000 --> 0:15:46,000
