284
0:15:46.584,000 --> 0:15:48,000
this is not a political issue.

285
0:15:48.773,000 --> 0:15:53,000
Again, the Republicans here -- this shouldn't be partisan.

286
0:15:54.336,000 --> 0:15:57,000
You have more influence than some of us who are Democrats do.

287
0:15:58.421,000 --> 0:15:59,000
This is an opportunity.

288
0:15:59.921,000 --> 0:16:03,000
Not just this, but connected to the ideas that are here,

289
0:16:04.797,000 --> 0:16:05,000
to bring more coherence to them.

290
0:16:07.495,000 --> 0:16:08,000
We are one.

291
0:16:09.065,000 --> 0:16:11,000
Thank you very much, I appreciate it.

292
